en_228409_0	HE the President Maithripala Sirisena Commander in Chief of the Armed Forces, in what can be regarded as a New Year bonanza has promoted Brigadier M.A.A.D Sirinaga, Director Electrical & Mechanical Engineering to the rank of Major General along with 66 other Senior Officers to the rank of Colonels and Lieutenant Colonels effective from specific dates, clearing a much - anticipated backlog in their career prospects.
en_228409_1	Those promotions have been approved by the President on the recommendations of the Ministry Of Defence and the Commander of the Army Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake.
